        To request transfers of training sessions or to transfer your ticket to someone else,  <a href="mailto:events@tilde.io?subject=RustConf Transfer Request">email the team the following details about the replacement attendee</a>, from the email address of either the ticket purchaser or holder:
        <ul>
          <li>
            Full Name
          </li>
          <li>
            Email Address
          </li>
          <li>
            GitHub username
          </li>
          <li>
            Dietary restrictions
          </li>
